### Get published events sorted by startDate
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=status eq 'Published'&$orderby=startDate

### Get workshop events
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=eventType eq 'Workshop'

### Get registrations for event e1
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Registrations?$filter=eventId eq 'e1'

### Get speakers sorted by rating
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Speakers?$orderby=rating desc

### Get events with available seats
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events?$filter=registeredCount lt maxAttendees

### POST new registration
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Registrations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID":"r11",
  "eventId":"e1",
  "attendeeName":"Test User",
  "attendeeEmail":"test@gmail.com",
  "attendeePhone":"9999999999",
  "company":"OpenAI",
  "ticketType":"General",
  "registrationDate":"2026-06-01",
  "status":"Confirmed",
  "amountPaid":1500,
  "paymentId":"PAY011"
}

### PATCH event status Draft -> Published
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Events('e3')
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status":"Published"
}

### POST feedback
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/event/Feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ID":"f4",
  "eventId":"e1",
  "attendeeEmail":"test@gmail.com",
  "overallRating":5,
  "contentRating":5,
  "venueRating":4,
  "speakerRating":5,
  "comment":"Excellent session",
  "submittedAt":"2026-06-11T10:00:00Z"
}